[TAG:DISCORD,AVIATION,BOT,COMMANDS][DESC:Slash Command mentions use the following format: </airportinfo>, </descent> - Basic Descent Profile Calculator, </metar-taf>, </newsky> - Newsky is a VA platform, </ivao> - Get IVAO Informations, </vatsim> - Get VATSIM Informations, </simbrief> - Display a SimBrief flight plan in Discord, </weather> - Regional weather report, </flightinfo> - Information regarding actual, real flights, </vatsim-connect> - Connect to Vatsim and sync Vatsim Ratings to Discord Roles </calculator calculator> - Aviation related unit converter and calculator];
